metadata.name: ∞ Goddess of the Sun ∞
metadata.description:
∞ The Goddess of the Sun opens and fills the heart with Love, brings light, protects and fills with energy!
Turn to the Goddess when you need more love, self-love, inspiration in your life, reconnect with your own inner world, light up your life path!
Feel this light of the Goddess and let it into your soul, be filled with love, energy and strength. Know its nature, essence, strength and power! Open yourself and your heart and you will see a new beautiful world! The mighty Powers of the Goddess are capable of anything!!! ∞
The collector will receive a full meditation with a description in high quality 4k!
